⚖️ os vs pathlib

| Feature | os Module | pathlib |
|----------|-----------|----------|
| Style | Functional | Object-Oriented |
| Readability | Moderate | High |
| Modern Usage | Older | Recommended |
| Cross Platform | Yes | Yes |
| Path Operations | More Complex | Easier |

